### Test Update Payment - All Fields

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3005/api
@adminToken = your_admin_token_here
@paymentId = your_payment_id_here

### 1. Test Update Payment dengan Semua Field
PUT {{baseUrl}}/payments/{{paymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 2750000,
  "method": "credit_card",
  "status": "pending",
  "transactionId": "TXN20240115002",
  "notes": "Updated payment amount - termasuk asuransi"
}

### 2. Test Update Payment - Hanya Amount dan Method
PUT {{baseUrl}}/payments/{{paymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 3000000,
  "method": "bank_transfer"
}

### 3. Test Update Payment - Hanya Status dan Notes
PUT {{baseUrl}}/payments/{{paymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "paid",
  "notes": "Payment sudah lunas"
}

### 4. Test Update Payment - Semua Field Kecuali Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/payments/{{paymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 2500000,
  "method": "e_wallet",
  "transactionId": "GOPAY123456789",
